{"tid":1063686,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"FIFA宣佈世冠盃擴充至24隊","createTime":"2019-03-16T03:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T10:46:53.000Z","uid":3454,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e99c6077fc5af20875ddcb4798e11d2d714b1250","tid":1063686,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:15:26.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=hEl8YzVD%2FOsYsQiwoICJnCF8jviwHHlsaTD6zKFHFMM%3D&h=fa0930b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】國際足協周五宣佈，同意把2021年世界冠軍球會盃擴張至24隊出戰，被一眾歐洲強隊大力反對。<br />\n<br />\n現時的世界冠軍球會盃只有7支球隊參加，每年於12月舉行，歐聯、南美自由盃冠軍球隊直入4強，只需要出戰2場比賽。不過，在新制之下，賽事將會移師6至7月，而且比賽場數亦肯定更多。<br />\n<br />\n國際足協會長恩芬天奴（Gianni Infantino）直言，不少歐洲強隊都不滿意這個改動，聲明不會參賽，曼聯、巴塞隆拿、皇家馬德里、巴黎聖日耳門等列強，更聯署去信FIFA。<br />\n<br />\n「我們希望所有強隊都參戰，曾經跟歐洲足協溝通過，結果很正面。我們的責任是作決定，因為需要處理籌劃事宜，只餘下2年時間。現在，全世界將會看到一個真正的世冠盃，世界最佳球隊決出真正的世界冠軍。」恩芬天奴說。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/mobileweb/news/details?id=24891101527\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fmobileweb%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D24891101527&d=hEl8YzVD%2FOsYsQiwoICJnCF8jviwHHlsaTD6zKFHFMM%3D&h=b39dfe4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/mobileweb/news/details?id=24891101527</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想踢能死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c034aa718af0e91e4503ec43f6c78be20adfccd","tid":1063686,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:17:15.000Z","msg":"One more fish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c1e311554b0c49d6940335ffdc6ccd96074c14","tid":1063686,"uid":197125,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:17:48.000Z","msg":"同意加隊，但要改為4年一度"},{"pid":"b6f67eb8fc57baea463bf6eeda060fd1343b6d0d","tid":1063686,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03: